{"id": "hsn1665702783399", "title": "scan (deprecated)", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "scan (deprecated)"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hsn1665702783399.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">scan (deprecated)</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: run (deprecated)   \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: run (deprecated)   \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qiy1665703006046.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: scope…endscope \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: scope…endscope \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xxm1665702583457.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/hsn1665702783399.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/hsn1665702783399.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/hsn1665702783399.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528355\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528355\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 12, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hsn1665702783399.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsn1665702783399.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsn1665702783399.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hsn1665702783399\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__scan_237948\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Scans a field or variable for a specified profile and returns the starting position of the profile.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__topic_d76853e1_d76854e1_d76855e1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__note_n1z_qx2_vzb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">scan</code> statement is deprecated. It has been\n            superseded by<code class=\"ph codeph\"> $scan</code> function, which is applicable to all component\n            types.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76856e1_d76857e1_d76858e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">scan</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__section_w2169ab1b7b5_w2170ab1b7_w2171ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76859e1_d76860e1_d76861e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">scan vString ,\"house\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__topic_d50527e1_d50528e1_d50529e1_d50530e1_d50531e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d122432e91\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__3\">\n Field or variable to be scanned. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> is a Date, Time, or Datetime field, Uniface first converts the value to a string according to the default format from the language setup before performing the scan.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1__entry__3\">\n String or syntax string, with a maximum length of 256 characters, that contains the profile to be matched.\n <p class=\"p\">A syntax string is enclosed in single quotation marks (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">' '</span>) or using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$syntax</span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__topic_d50532e1_d50533e1_d50534e1_d50535e1_d50536e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d122432e172\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76868e1_d76869e1_d76870e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">scan</span> has no effect on <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1__entry__2\">\n Starting position in <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> of the first match.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsn1665702783399__table_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1__entry__2\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var> not found or <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> is an empty string (\"\").\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__topic_d50537e1_d50538e1_d50539e1_d50540e1_d50541e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d122432e250\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__topic_d50542e1_d50543e1_d50544e1_d50545e1_d50546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d122432e259\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76880e1_d76881e1_d76882e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">scan</span> statement returns the position of the first character of <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> that matches the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var> provided. (The first character of a string is at position 1.)</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76883e1_d76884e1_d76885e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var> is a normal string, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">scan</span> looks for an exact, case-sensitive match of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var> in <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76886e1_d76887e1_d76888e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">Profile</var> is a syntax string, the match is not case sensitive. Lowercase is seen as both uppercase and lowercase, and uppercase is seen as uppercase only.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76889e1_d76890e1_d76891e1\">You can use single quotes or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$syntax</span> to specify a syntax string. Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$syntax</span> to perform case-insensitive scans when the string contains diacritics (for example an umlaut).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__p_d76892e1_d76893e1_d76894e1\">If character attributes (bold, underline, and so on) are specified in the profile string, Uniface ignores them. In this case, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">abc</span> (bold) is the same as <code class=\"ph codeph\">abc</code> (not bold). The asterisk wildcard (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">*</span>) in Uniface stands for 0- n characters, so spaces also qualify in the syntax check. However, one asterisk in the syntax string causes Uniface to check only the following 32 characters.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__section_lvf_dzl_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d122432e320\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">scan</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following examples show different ways of using the\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">scan</span> statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hsn1665702783399__pre_yvs_dzl_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vString = \"Nibble1\"\nNAME = \"Myrtle\"\nscan vString ,\"bbl\" ; $result = 3\nscan vString ,\"house\" ; $result = 0 (string not found)\nscan vString ,'#' ; $result = 7 (first number in string)\nscan NAME,\"yr*e\" ; $result = 0\n; (syntax strings must be in single quotes)\nscan NAME,'yr*e' ; $result = 2 (syntax strings allowed)\nscan vString , NAME[5,6] ; $result = 5 (scan vString , \"le\")\nvString2 =\"schön\"\nscan vString2 , $syntax(\"hö*\") ; $result=3\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hha1720076228830.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>length (deprecated)</a><p>Return the number of characters in the specified string.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqr1665702555238.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$syntax</a><p>Convert a string to a syntax string.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdy1714482565238.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$scan</a><p>Returns the position of a substring within a string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528355\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528355\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "scan (deprecated) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Scans a field or variable for a specified profile and returns the starting position of the profile. Note: The scan statement is deprecated. It has been superseded by $scan function, which is applicable to all component types. scan String , Profile Example: scan vString ,\"house\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String Field or variable to be scanned. If String is a Date, Time, or Datetime field, Uniface first converts the value to a string according to the default format from the language setup before performing the scan. Profile String String or syntax string, with a maximum length of 256 characters, that contains the profile to be matched. A syntax string is enclosed in single quotation marks ( ' ' ) or using $syntax . Return Values scan has no effect on $status . Table 2. Values returned in $result Value Meaning >0 Starting position in String of the first match. 0 Profile not found or String is an empty string (\"\"). Use Allowed in all component types. Description The scan statement returns the position of the first character of String that matches the Profile provided. (The first character of a string is at position 1.) If Profile is a normal string, scan looks for an exact, case-sensitive match of Profile in String . If Profile is a syntax string, the match is not case sensitive. Lowercase is seen as both uppercase and lowercase, and uppercase is seen as uppercase only. You can use single quotes or $syntax to specify a syntax string. Use $syntax to perform case-insensitive scans when the string contains diacritics (for example an umlaut). If character attributes (bold, underline, and so on) are specified in the profile string, Uniface ignores them. In this case, abc (bold) is the same as abc (not bold). The asterisk wildcard ( * ) in Uniface stands for 0- n characters, so spaces also qualify in the syntax check. However, one asterisk in the syntax string causes Uniface to check only the following 32 characters. Example: Using scan The following examples show different ways of using the scan statement: vString = \"Nibble1\" NAME = \"Myrtle\" scan vString ,\"bbl\" ; $result = 3 scan vString ,\"house\" ; $result = 0 (string not found) scan vString ,'#' ; $result = 7 (first number in string) scan NAME,\"yr*e\" ; $result = 0 ; (syntax strings must be in single quotes) scan NAME,'yr*e' ; $result = 2 (syntax strings allowed) scan vString , NAME[5,6] ; $result = 5 (scan vString , \"le\") vString2 =\"schön\" scan vString2 , $syntax(\"hö*\") ; $result=3 Copy Related Links length (deprecated) Return the number of characters in the specified string. $syntax Convert a string to a syntax string. $scan Returns the position of a substring within a string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}